graph TB
    subgraph "Kueue Component"
        Controller[kueue-controller-manager<br/>Deployment]
        WebhookSvc[webhook-service<br/>ClusterIP 443/TCP]
        MetricsSvc[metrics-service<br/>ClusterIP 8443/TCP]

        subgraph "Core Components"
            WorkloadReconciler[Workload Reconciler]
            CQReconciler[ClusterQueue Reconciler]
            LQReconciler[LocalQueue Reconciler]
            Scheduler[Scheduler]
            Cache[In-Memory Cache]
        end

        subgraph "Job Integrations"
            BatchIntegration[Batch Jobs]
            KubeflowIntegration[Kubeflow Jobs]
            RayIntegration[Ray Jobs]
            JobSetIntegration[JobSet]
            AppWrapperIntegration[AppWrapper]
        end

        Controller -->|manages| WorkloadReconciler
        Controller -->|manages| CQReconciler
        Controller -->|manages| LQReconciler
        Controller -->|uses| Scheduler
        Controller -->|uses| Cache
        Controller -->|integrates| BatchIntegration
        Controller -->|integrates| KubeflowIntegration
        Controller -->|integrates| RayIntegration
        Controller -->|integrates| JobSetIntegration
        Controller -->|integrates| AppWrapperIntegration
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        Workload[Workload CRD]
        ClusterQueue[ClusterQueue CRD]
        LocalQueue[LocalQueue CRD]
        ResourceFlavor[ResourceFlavor CRD]
        AdmissionCheck[AdmissionCheck CRD]
        ProvisioningConfig[ProvisioningRequestConfig CRD]
        MultiKueueConfig[MultiKueueConfig CRD]
    end

    User[User] -->|creates Job| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    K8sAPI -->|webhook| WebhookSvc
    K8sAPI -->|watches| WorkloadReconciler

    WorkloadReconciler -->|creates| Workload
    Workload -->|assigned to| LocalQueue
    LocalQueue -->|maps to| ClusterQueue
    ClusterQueue -->|uses| ResourceFlavor
    ClusterQueue -->|requires| AdmissionCheck

    Scheduler -->|evaluates| Workload
    Scheduler -->|checks quota| ClusterQueue
    Scheduler -->|admits| K8sAPI

    Controller -->|creates| ProvisioningRequest[ProvisioningRequest]
    ProvisioningRequest -->|triggers| ClusterAutoscaler[Cluster Autoscaler]

    Controller -->|dispatches to| RemoteCluster[Remote K8s Cluster]
    MultiKueueConfig -->|configures| RemoteCluster

    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes| MetricsSvc

    CertManager[cert-manager] -->|provisions| WebhookCert[Webhook TLS Cert]

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px
    style Scheduler fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style Cache fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style Workload fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style ClusterQueue fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style LocalQueue fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style K8sAPI fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style ClusterAutoscaler fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style CertManager fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Prometheus fill:#999,stroke:#333
